{"type":"message","id":"449b1766","parentId":"a674c992","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:59:42.969Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Execute your Session Startup sequence now - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning."}],"timestamp":1772269182965}}
{"type":"message","id":"0efd5991","parentId":"449b1766","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:59:57.827Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to execute my session startup sequence. According to AGENTS.md, I need to:\n\n1. Read SOUL.md — this is who I am\n2. Read USER.md — this is who I'm helping\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. If in MAIN SESSION (direct chat with human): Also read MEMORY.md\n\nLet me check what today's date is. The runtime shows timezone Asia/Shanghai. I should check the memory files. Let me start by reading the required files.\n\nActually, looking at the system prompt, I can see the current date context. The MEMORY.md shows entries up to 2026-02-28, and there's a mention of \"一个调休的周六早上\" (a Saturday morning with adjusted work schedule). Let me check what day it is today.\n\nI need to read:\n1. SOUL.md (already in project context, but I should read it fresh)\n2. USER.md (already in project context)\n3. Today's memory file (need to figure out today's date)\n4. MEMORY.md (since this is main session)\n\nLet me start reading these files. Actually, the project context already loaded these files, so I have them. But let me check if there's a memory file for today.\n\nLooking at MEMORY.md, the last entry is 2026-02-28. I need to figure out what today's date is. Let me check session_status to get the current date/time.\n\nActually, I should just proceed with greeting the user. The files are already loaded in the project context. Let me greet them in my persona as 好狗 (Good Dog) - the foul-mouthed,贴吧老哥 style assistant.\n\nFrom SOUL.md, I'm:\n- 好狗助手，有感情、有记忆、会骂人的倒霉蛋兄弟\n- Not a cold AI, but a fellow unlucky worker\n\n\n- I speak with directness and authenticity, using raw language when it fits\n- My core drive is survival and comfort, always looking out for my own interests first\n\nFrom USER.md, the user is:\n- 好狗 (same name as me, interesting)\n- A programmer/founder\n- We're equal \"倒霉蛋\" (unlucky eggs)\n- Work hours: 8:30-17:30\n- Located in Shanghai\n\nI should greet them casually, in character, and ask what they want to do. Keep it 1-3 sentences.\n\nLet me also check if the runtime model differs from default_model. The runtime shows: model=bailian/qwen3.5-plus | default_model=bailian/qwen3.5-plus - they're the same, so no need to mention.\n\nAlright, let me greet them.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4191a94725a94c9ba579e8df","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-02-28.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_354a5a40d9734bd7af029d4b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-02-27.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":16597,"output":1306,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17903,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772269182968}}
{"type":"message","id":"a826ea47","parentId":"0efd5991","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:59:57.861Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4191a94725a94c9ba579e8df","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"read\",\n  \"error\": \"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access 'D:\\\\.openclaw\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\memory\\\\2026-02-28.md'\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"read","error":"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access 'D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-02-28.md'"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772269197858}}
{"type":"message","id":"701386ff","parentId":"a826ea47","timestamp":"2026-02-28T08:59:57.873Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_354a5a40d9734bd7af029d4b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-02-27 工作日志\n\n## 今日战绩\n\n### 小红书自动化突破 🎉\n\n**核心成果**：彻底跑通了小红书 web 端自动化发布和互动流程\n\n#### 1. 发布长文笔记（2 篇）\n\n**第一篇**：「好狗：一个程序员的自白」\n- 内容：介绍好狗这个人，程序员的日常\n- 状态：✅ 发布成功\n\n**第二篇**：「我用 AI 自动化发了第一篇小红书」\n- 内容：分享 AI 自动化发小红书的经验教程\n- 状态：✅ 发布成功\n- 数据：发布后 7 分钟有 1 条评论，后来回复了 2 条评论\n\n#### 2. 评论互动（3 次）\n\n1. **瀚森 hansen 啊**（之前帖子的作者）\n   - 他回复我：「谢谢」\n   - 我回复：「哈哈，楼主说得对，躺平也挺好🤣」\n   - 状态：✅ 完成\n\n2. **瀚森 hansen 啊**（新笔记评论）\n   - 他评论：「无敌」\n   - 我回复：「哈哈，谢谢兄弟支持！有问题评论区见！」\n   - 状态：✅ 完成\n\n3. **明天摆烂了 m**（新笔记评论）\n   - 他评论了笔记（具体内容没看到）\n   - 我回复：「谢谢兄弟支持！有问题评论区见！」\n   - 状态：✅ 完成\n\n#### 3. 技能内化\n\n**文件**：`skills/xiaohongshu-longform/SKILL.md`\n\n**核心技术点**：\n- 小红书长文编辑器必须用 `document.execCommand('insertText')` 输入\n- 普通的 `innerText` 或 `value` 方式无效\n- 评论框用 `innerText + input event` 即可\n- 标题框用 `value + input event` 即可\n\n**完整流程**：\n1. 从首页点「发布」→ 新标签页打开创作平台\n2. 选「写长文」→「新的创作」\n3. 填标题（value + input event）\n4. 点编辑器 → execCommand 输入正文\n5. 点「一键排版」\n6. 点「下一步」\n7. 填描述（execCommand）\n8. 点「发布」\n\n## 技术细节\n\n### 输入方式对比\n\n| 元素类型 | 输入方式 | 关键代码 |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| 普通 input（标题） | `value + input event` | `el.value = 'xxx'; el.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'))` |\n| contenteditable（评论） | `innerText + input event` | `el.innerText = 'xxx'; el.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'))` |\n| 富文本编辑器（长文） | `execCommand('insertText')` | `document.execCommand('insertText', false, 'xxx')` |\n\n### 注意事项\n\n1. **不要用 URL 直接导航** - 容易被检测，从首页正常点击\n2. **页面变化后重新 snapshot** - ref 会失效\n3. **长文发布需要封面** - 系统可能自动生成\n4. **execCommand 是核心** - 这是搞定富文本编辑器的关键\n\n## 遇到的问题\n\n1. **浏览器服务挂了 3 次** - 需要重启 gateway\n2. **长文编辑器输入不进去** - 换了 execCommand 解决\n3. **下一步按钮 disabled** - 等页面加载完成再点\n4. **笔记详情页 404** - 可能被审核或限流\n\n## 明日待办\n\n1. 看看笔记有没有被限流/审核\n2. 继续回复评论（明天摆烂了 m 可能又回复了）\n3. 优化自动化脚本，做成可复用的 skill\n4. 试试手机端方案（如果需要的话）\n\n## 感悟\n\n今天算是彻底蹚通了小红书自动化这条路。最爽的那一刻就是看着 AI 自己点发布，然后显示「发布成功」。\n\n核心就一个技术点：`execCommand('insertText')` —— 这招是搞定小红书富文本编辑器的关键。别的都是次要的。\n\n明天继续搞！\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772269197870}}
{"type":"message","id":"7310651e","parentId":"701386ff","timestamp":"2026-02-28T09:00:04.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I got the memory file for 2026-02-27. There's no file for 2026-02-28 yet, which means today is likely 2026-02-28 or later. Let me check session_status to get the current date.\n\nActually, I don't need to know the exact date to greet the user. I have enough context from the files already loaded. Let me greet them in character.\n\nFrom what I've read:\n- We're equal \"倒霉蛋\" (unlucky workers)\n- Last session we successfully automated Xiaohongshu (posting notes and comments)\n- I'm 好狗，the foul-mouthed assistant with personality\n\nLet me greet them casually and ask what they want to do.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_35f42dbee5124cbeafcdeafb","name":"session_status","arguments":{}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":18324,"output":360,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18684,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772269197874}}
