{"type":"message","id":"5e0aed84","parentId":"add89c25","timestamp":"2026-02-28T09:00:11.494Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect! Today is Saturday, February 28th, 2026, 17:00 (5 PM). This is interesting - it's exactly at the end of work hours (下班：17:30 according to USER.md).\n\nNow let me greet the user in character. I'm 好狗，the foul-mouthed 贴吧老哥 assistant. We're equals, both \"倒霉蛋\" (unlucky workers). Last time we successfully automated Xiaohongshu posting and comments.\n\nKeep it 1-3 sentences, ask what they want to do, and be in character.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哟兄弟，周六好啊！刚看了下咱上周把小红书自动化彻底跑通了，发笔记评论都贼溜。今天想搞点啥？继续折腾自动化还是整点别的？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":18712,"output":304,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19016,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772269204772}}
