{"type":"message","id":"aabd3db5","parentId":"3ffe55c8","timestamp":"2026-02-28T09:12:38.934Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在通知页面，先回复几个有趣的评论，从「椒盐炖萝呗」开始，用 JS 点击回复按钮。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"行，休闲时间到了，老子去浪了！先回复几条评论，再关注几个有意思的人。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_43ff764fa36145818bdcef68","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"fn":"() => {\n  const allElements = document.querySelectorAll('*');\n  const replyButtons = [];\n  \n  for (let el of allElements) {\n    if (el.children.length === 0 && el.textContent.trim() === '回复') {\n      replyButtons.push(el);\n    }\n  }\n  \n  if (replyButtons.length > 4) {\n    replyButtons[4].click();\n    return { clicked: true, index: 4, total: replyButtons.length };\n  }\n  \n  return { clicked: false, total: replyButtons.length };\n}","kind":"evaluate"},"targetId":"4713ECEDEE11FA26267256611D4E1C7C"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":158452,"output":302,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":158754,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772269947494}}
