{"type":"message","id":"5b8ad93b","parentId":"65b5ebd1","timestamp":"2026-02-28T09:18:03.916Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说我点帖子不熟练，让我先关闭没用的网站，然后去小红书主页点一个帖子并评论。我现在已经在小红书推荐流页面了，需要：\n\n1. 先点进一个帖子（要用/explore/链接，不是作者链接）\n2. 滚动到页面底部找到评论框\n3. 点击评论框→输入评论→发送\n\n让我选一个帖子点进去，比如第一个「求助」或者找个别的话题感兴趣的。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c741dd0e85564a2baf28530e","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"kind":"click","ref":"e33"},"targetId":"4713ECEDEE11FA26267256611D4E1C7C"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":215865,"output":285,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":216150,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772270246929}}
